#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Kirjeldus"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is a program which shows you the Periodic System of the Elements "
"(PSE). You can use &kalzium; to search for information about the elements or "
"to learn facts about the PSE."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; on keemiliste elementide perioodilisussüsteemi (Mendelejevi "
"tabelit) näitav rakendus. &kalzium; võimaldab nii otsida infot keemiliste "
"elementide kohta kui ka õppida tundma Mendelejevi tabelit."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; provides you with all kinds of information about the PSE. You can "
"look up lots of information about the elements and also use visualisations "
"to show them."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; pakub perioodilisustabeli kohta kõikvõimalikku infot. Kõik "
"keemilised elemendid on varustatud ohtra infomaterjaliga, elementidega "
"tutvumiseks saab kasutada ka visuaalseid abivahendeid."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This package is part of the official KDE edutainment module."
msgstr "See pakett kuulub KDE mängu ja kooli mooduli kdeedu koosseisu."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Võtmed"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "--molecule <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "--molecule <replaceable>failinimi</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the given molecule file in cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, chm, cdx, cdxml, "
"c3d1, c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, gam, inp, gamin, "
"gamout, tmol, fract, mpd, or mol2 format."
msgstr ""
"Määratud molekuli avamine cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, chm, cdx, cdxml, c3d1, "
"c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, gam, inp, gamin, "
"gamout, tmol, fract, mpd või mol2 vormingus."

